During a recent screen of power usage I found the EuclidSeq to be by far the highest power user, nearly 100mA, where other analog modules used < 20 mA, and other Arduino based modules drawing 30 to 50 mA. My highest drawing modules are vacuum tube heating elements at 175 mA. \
\
